Global Over Bed Pole Hoist Market Insights
Over Bed Pole Hoist Market size was valued at USD 0.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.45 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Over Bed Pole Hoist Market Overview
The global over bed pole hoist market was valued at approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2024, with projections to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period of 2025-2030. The growth of the market is attributed to the increasing demand for advanced healthcare solutions, particularly in hospitals and home care settings. Over bed pole hoists are critical in patient handling, ensuring safe lifting, transferring, and repositioning, which is driving their adoption globally. With technological advancements and increasing healthcare spending, the market is expected to witness significant growth in the coming years.

